  "instruction": "A local build brief is already available in Chrome at file:///home/user/Desktop/ops_signal_board_brief.html. Use VS Code to build /home/user/Desktop/ops_signal_board into a previewable ops dashboard from the provided local data.json and assets/ops-badge.svg. Create index.html, styles.css, app.js, and manifest.json. Load data.json with fetch(), render a hero area, a filter bar with buttons All, Active, and Risk, a KPI grid in #kpi-grid, an incident timeline in #incident-timeline, a canvas chart in canvas#chartCanvas, and a side drawer as aside#detail-drawer. Use the local badge asset in the header or hero area. Manifest must set project to ops-signal-board, theme to midnight-signal, chartType to bar, dataSource to data.json, and previewPort to 8125. Start a local preview server and finish with Chrome open at http://127.0.0.1:8125/index.html. Keep all assets local.",
